getInstance

public static PwCoreSession getInstance()
Return an instance of PwCoreSession. This will provide a handle to be able to start and stop sessions.

Returns:
A Core session instance.
See Also:
CoreSessionImp.activityStartSession(android.content.Context), CoreSessionImp.activityStopSession(android.content.Context)

killSession

public static void killSession()
This will completely wipe out all session related data as well as keys. If this is called, CoreSessionImp.registerKeys(android.content.Context, String, String, String) must be called again to start a new session.
